def get_processed_request(self, request: Request, response: Response) ->(
    Request | None):
    if len(request.url) <= self.maxlength:
        return request
    logger.info('Ignoring link (url length > %(maxlength)d): %(url)s ', {
        'maxlength': self.maxlength, 'url': request.url}, extra={'spider':
        self.crawler.spider})
    assert self.crawler.stats
    self.crawler.stats.inc_value('urllength/request_ignored_count', spider=
        self.crawler.spider)
    return None
